    <h1>Lava Lolegaon Rishap Itinerary - 3 Days, 2 Nights</h1>







    <h2>Day 1: Arrival in Lava</h2>



    <p>Upon arrival in Lava, check-in at your hotel and take some time to rest. In the afternoon, visit the following attractions:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Neora Valley National Park</strong> - Explore the rich biodiversity and scenic beauty of the park.</li>



      <li><strong>Lava Monastery</strong> - Visit the peaceful Kagyu Thekchen Ling Monastery.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Return to your hotel for dinner and overnight stay.</p>







    <h2>Day 2: Lava to Lolegaon</h2>



    <p>After breakfast, check-out from the hotel and proceed to Lolegaon. On the way, visit:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Changey Waterfall</strong> - A beautiful waterfall surrounded by lush greenery.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Upon arrival in Lolegaon, check-in at your hotel and explore:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Canopy Walk</strong> - Experience the famous hanging bridge walk.</li>



      <li><strong>Jhandi Dara</strong> - Enjoy panoramic views of the Himalayas.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Return to your hotel for dinner and overnight stay.</p>







    <h2>Day 3: Lolegaon to Rishap and Departure</h2>



    <p>After breakfast, check-out from the hotel and proceed to Rishap. Spend the day exploring:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Tiffin Dara</strong> - A viewpoint offering stunning views of the Kanchenjunga range.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Proceed to your onward journey in the evening.</p>







